::Feline::
She looked at HotRod, "Good, 4 bots in the Brig.  We can surely use 
them.  We will need Cybersharks help on this, but we should try to 
get them."

Battera::
She stepped out of the CR chamber, fullu healled.
"Zardus, please advise on statis of the battle."

KitKat::
She stepped out of the CR and saw Drillbit sleeping next to the 
chamber.  She lightly kissed his cheek. She smiled, he looked so 
peacefull when he slept.

Squizzy::
She was starting to wake up in the CR chamber.  She was very groggy 
and could barely open her eyes. 

SnowCat::
She walked to the entrance of the ship and looked around.
